                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-10-defend148 t18180114-10-punish58"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Abbott.</p>
